    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_037</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、空が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>L-Look in the sky! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279276</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_036</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、何が起きたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What just happened!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_038</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おかーさーん、こわいよ−</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mommy, I'm scared! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしの……魔術が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Did my magic...just...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしのせい……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is this...all my fault...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え、えっと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、まだそうと
決まったわけじゃないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's not jump to conclusions just yet. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_005Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『虹輪（プリズムリング）』が
発生するなんて！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Prism Ring has appeared! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_006Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これは大きい！
大変だぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's huge! This'll get 
really dangerous! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281572</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんた、誰……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey! You! Who are you? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281712</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_008Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私は&lt;Red&gt;オリーブヴィレッジ&lt;White&gt;に
住む魔術師だ。
魔法力の研究をしている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm a well-versed sorcerer from Olive Village. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……『虹輪』って何ですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's this "Prism Ring" you are talking about? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_010Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>凝縮したマナの塊が、
魔法力を得て
虹色の輪になるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm afraid it's a giant cluster of Mana. It surges from a 
strong interaction of magic energy resulting in a rainbow colored column. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_011Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>近くのマナを吸収して、
どんどん大きくなっていくのさ。</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It'll gradually absorb all the Mana within its range,
growing bigger and stronger in the process. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282236</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふーん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Umm... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_013Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほうっておいたら世界中の
マナを吸い尽くしてしまう……
魔術が暴走するなんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At this rate, it's likely all the Mana from this world will be drained, exhausting its supplies... Then, unable to control
its magic, the Prism Ring will enter a wild rampage... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282780</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, that's... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうすれば、
止められるんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is there any way to stop it? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_016Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>虹輪は
地水火風の４つの力が
混ざり合ったものだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Prism Ring might be stopped by combining the powers of Earth, Water, Fire and Wind. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_017Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……四大精霊の力を
借りられたらいいんだが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...You might be able to borrow the powers
of the Four Elemental Summon Spirits, but... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>四大精霊……
あの、それはどこに！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Four Elemental Summon Spirits... Please
tell me, where to find them! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_019Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>伝承として伝えられているが、
実際に会った者はいない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've heard rumors but I've never actually met them. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_020</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is starting to sound like a real pain... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_021Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔女の塔にブライトローズという
魔女が住んでいると
聞いたことがある。</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's a magician that goes by the name of Bright Rose 
living in a tower nearby. It wouldn't hurt to pay her a visit. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284560</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_022</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ブライト……ローズ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Bright...Rose? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_023Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これはもしかすると
あの魔女の仕業かも
しれないな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't know about her, personally, 
but it's as good a lead as any... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_024</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なぁ、おっさん。
魔女の塔ってドコに
あるんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, grandpa, where can I find this magician's tower? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_025Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここから東の方向で、
別名&lt;Red&gt;きらめきの塔&lt;White&gt;と呼ばれている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you travel east from here you'll bump
into a tower named "Glimmer Spire." </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_026Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きみたち行くつもりなのかい。
危険かもしれないから
気をつけるんだぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm not certain what dangers await you there
but if you intend to go please be careful. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_027</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ、ちょっと、
その魔女んとこ、
行ってくる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right, let's go to where that magician is. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_028</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行ってくるって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You...really want to go there... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_029</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そいつに聞きゃ、
あれ消せるかもだし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You heard the dude already. 
I need to dispel this thing. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_030</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それと、
困ってる人助けんのが
オレらの仕事なんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>‘Sides helping people in need is my job, isn't it? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_031</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……わたしも行くよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I'm going with you. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_034</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you say so... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_040_035C</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んじゃ、行こうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go, then! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
